现在我们准备回到NFT管理器合约中的tokenURI函数，并添加实际的渲染： function tokenURI(uint256 tokenId) public view override returns (string memory)
{ TokenPosition memory tokenPosition = positions[tokenId]; if (tokenPosition.pool == address(0x00)) revert WrongToken(); IUniswapV3Pool pool = IUniswapV3Pool(tokenPosition.pool); return NFTRenderer.render( NFTRenderer.RenderParams({ pool: tokenPosition.pool, owner: address(this), lowerTick: tokenPosition.lowerTick, upperTick: tokenPosition.upperTick, fee: pool.fee() }) );
}

